div.p:
Then the King ariseth and is led to the Communion Table, where he
makes a Solemn Oath, in sight of all the People, to observe the Premises;
and laying his hand upon the Book, saith,

                  Char. Thus far (says he) we have given the Pourtraicture of a Popish
King: And now, let us take a draught of his Features in his Minority;
that is, while he is only a Popish Heir Apparent, I.d.
